    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      146.72,
      526.48,
      160.34
    ],
    "text": "General of the Department of Wildlife Conservation (hereinafter referred to as \u2018the DG\u2019),",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      167.6,
      526.22,
      181.22
    ],
    "text": "without the conduct of a proper inquiry, constitutes a violation of his fundamental rights",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      188.36,
      526.33,
      201.98
    ],
    "text": "guaranteed under Articles 12(1) and 14(1)(g) of the Constitution. This Court granted leave",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      209.24,
      443.68,
      222.86
    ],
    "text": "to proceed in respect of the alleged infringements under the said Articles.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      241.91,
      526.48,
      255.53
    ],
    "text": "The material facts are largely undisputed. The Petitioner appeared for an interview",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      262.67,
      526.22,
      276.29
    ],
    "text": "conducted by the Department of Wildlife Conservation (\u2018Department\u2019) on 13 February",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      283.43,
      526.24,
      297.05
    ],
    "text": "2019, pursuant to Gazette Notification No. 2059 dated 16 February 2018 (marked \u2018X2\u2019),",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      304.19,
      526.48,
      317.81
    ],
    "text": "which called for applications for recruitment to the post of Wildlife Forest Ranger Grade",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      325.07,
      526.22,
      338.69
    ],
    "text": "III through an open competitive examination. At the interview, the Petitioner produced",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      345.83,
      526.5,
      359.45
    ],
    "text": "his G.C.E. A/L (General Certificate of Education - Advanced Level - Examination)",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      366.59,
      526.15,
      380.21
    ],
    "text": "results for the year 2008, wherein he had obtained three Simple Passes in Physics,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      387.35,
      526.48,
      400.97
    ],
    "text": "Chemistry, and Biology, together with his G.C.E. O/L (General Certificate of Education",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      408.25,
      318.73,
      421.87
    ],
    "text": "- Ordinary Level - Examination) results of 2003.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      440.89,
      526.21,
      454.51
    ],
    "text": "At the said interview, the Petitioner was requested to furnish proof of having obtained a",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      461.65,
      526.15,
      475.27
    ],
    "text": "Credit Pass in Biology at the G.C.E. (Advanced Level) Examination. In response, he",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      482.53,
      526.5,
      496.15
    ],
    "text": "submitted his results from the 2007 G.C.E. A/L, at which he had secured a Credit Pass in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      503.29,
      526.22,
      516.91
    ],
    "text": "Biology but had failed the remaining subjects, namely Physics, Chemistry, and General",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      524.05,
      526.37,
      537.67
    ],
    "text": "English. Upon consideration of the results of the competitive examination held on 22 July",
