      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      167.12,
      526.16,
      180.74
    ],
    "text": "(ii) although the Petitioner had obtained a Credit Pass in Biology in 2007, he had",
