      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      580.36,
      526.1,
      593.98
    ],
    "text": "In this regard, I find no legal basis for the invocation of Clause 3.2 of Chapter V of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      601.12,
      526.31,
      614.74
    ],
