    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      125.48,
      526.14,
      139.1
    ],
    "text": "In these circumstances, the reversion of the Petitioner and his reappointment as a new",
