      200.24,
      526.13,
      213.86
    ],
    "text": "384) to contend that two wrongs do not make a right and that the right to equality does",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      221.0,
      526.41,
      234.62
    ],
    "text": "not extend to equal illegality (Dissanayake v Priyal de Silva [2007] 2 Sri LR 135). Likewise,",
