    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      326.15,
      368.65,
      339.77
    ],
    "text": "well established, they are inapplicable to the present case.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      358.79,
      526.19,
      372.41
    ],
    "text": "There is no evidence that the Petitioner procured his appointment through fraud or",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      379.55,
      526.21,
      393.17
    ],
    "text": "misrepresentation. On the contrary, he disclosed all relevant educational qualifications.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      400.33,
      526.48,
      413.95
    ],
    "text": "The error, if any, lies with the authorities who failed to properly scrutinise his credentials",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      421.09,
      526.28,
      434.71
    ],
    "text": "at the time of recruitment. In such circumstances, it would be manifestly unjust to deprive",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
